history.created_by: RUN /bin/sh -c apt-get install -y     libhdf5-dev     libcurl4-openssl-dev     libssl-dev     libpng-dev     libboost-all-dev     libxml2-dev     openjdk-8-jdk     python3-dev     python3-pip     wget     git     libfftw3-dev     libgsl-dev     pkg-config # buildkit
RUN /bin/sh -c git clone --branch v1.2.1 https://github.com/KlugerLab/FIt-SNE.git # buildkit
RUN /bin/sh -c g++ -std=c++11 -O3 FIt-SNE/src/sptree.cpp FIt-SNE/src/tsne.cpp FIt-SNE/src/nbodyfft.cpp  -o bin/fast_tsne -pthread -lfftw3 -lm # buildkit
RUN /bin/sh -c apt-get install -y     libgit2-dev     libfontconfig1-dev     libharfbuzz-dev     libfribidi-dev     libfreetype6-dev     libpng-dev     libtiff5-dev     libjpeg-dev # buildkit
